**/.git          ← don't copy git history into the image
**/.gitignore    ← don't copy gitignore files
**/.DS_Store     ← macOS junk files
**/*.swp         ← Vim swap files
**/*.swo         ← Vim swap files
**/*.log         ← log files

**/*.key         ← SSL private keys — NEVER bake these into an image
**/*.crt         ← SSL certificates — generated at runtime anyway
